#
# To add a new skill:
# 1. Create skill file in templates/skills/
# 2. Add entry to this manifest under skills:
# 3. Add skill to appropriate agents under agents:
# 4. Run install.sh to validate and deploy
#
# To validate the manifest:
# $ grep -h "^  - " templates/agents/*-concept.md | sort | uniq
# Compare output with skills listed in this file
#
# Priority Guidelines:
# - P0: Critical - Required for security/stability, used by 2+ agents
# - P1: Core - Essential for specific concept functionality
# - P2: Enhancement - Improves quality but not required
# - P3: Additional - Nice to have, low priority
# - Meta: Reference documentation, not directly used
